Class DescriptionTreeModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • model.DescriptionTreeModel

  • public class DescriptionTreeModel
extends java.util.Observable
    Author:
    Scott Spiers University of Strathclyde Final Year Project: Description Trees Supervisor: Sergey Kitaev The model for the application. Stores trees and restrictions. Provides tree generation functioanltiy as well as methods to get and add trees/restrictors
